{"tid":2032274,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［正視聽］反駁黃之鋒反對蘋果號召大家搵Trump一論","createTime":"2020-05-24T03:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T05:32:03.000Z","uid":270506,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7440aad023da24ac74f6be6f970554b8dda819","tid":2032274,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"呢件事無問題，本身Schumer 已經喺twitter屌緊Trump為香港做得唔夠，我地咁樣要Trump Save Hk/ liberate Hong Kong 反而民主黨又可能會攞多呢樣黎屌Trump見死不救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnkNTez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnkNTez.png&h=c4b9aaf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個行動只係我地請求Trump<strong>以美國總統身份</strong>幫我地，冇話到係叫Trump2020，唔係偏私Trump。反而係之鋒同佢班友反Trump反上腦，至會寫呢啲文，要知不嬲眾志班友係反Trump，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該叫佢哋解釋埋點解敖卓軒呢位比美國政界當係其中一位HK Protest Leader嘅人早前會幫Buttegieg呢位民主黨人助選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n結論：薑是老的辣，肥佬黎今次我撐你，之鋒唔該返去讀多啲書好好覺悟下<br />\n<br />\n要講靠邊站，香港眾志當之無愧<br />\n<br />\n揚言孤立中國 布蒂吉格持續撐港<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獲眾志點名支持</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20191221/COWS4MFAVJCJKFJE5DMCUFJZN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191221%2FCOWS4MFAVJCJKFJE5DMCUFJZN4%2F&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=7a86316b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191221%2FCOWS4MFAVJCJKFJE5DMCUFJZN4%2F&h=ac816ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20191221/COWS4MFAVJCJKFJE5DMCUFJZN4/</a>"},{"pid":"564e902ef483103a1de43751882f2fcbbaee3b43","tid":2032274,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望Spin 埋呢嗰po 就完</span>"},{"pid":"6417180f0e086824258e535f878de4ec8c7e9c69","tid":2032274,"uid":196